================================================================================================================
编译步骤
1,在当前目录下执行 make clean;make 命令可以编译出audio.ko
2,如果需要编译外部codec驱动，请进入 ex_codecs 目录，然后执行 make CODEC_NAME=xxx 编译出外部codec驱动 xxx_txx.ko

驱动加载
1, 如果使用外部codec， 请先加载外部codec驱动，后加载audio.ko
2, 如果不使用外部codec，只需加载audio.ko

以PRJ007外部codec es8389为例，vela板驱动加载命令：
	insmod es8389.ko gpio_func=1,2,0x000007c0
	insmod audio.ko excodec_name=es8389 excodec_addr=0x10 i2c_bus=0x2
================================================================================================================
Compilation steps
1. Execute make clean in the current directory; The make command can compile audio.ko
2. If you need to compile an external codec driver, please enter the ex_comdecs directory and execute make CODEC_NAME=xxx to compile the external codec driver xxx_txx.ko

Driver loading
1.If using an external codec, please load the external codec driver first, and then load audio.ko
2. If no external codec is used, simply load audio.ko

Taking PRJ007 external codec es8389 as an example, the command to load the Vela board driver is:
insmod es8389.ko gpio_func=1,2,0x000007c0
insmod audio.ko excodec_name=es8389 excodec_addr=0x10 i2c_bus=0x2
